title.narrative: Women for Health - Procurement of Services

description.narrative: This activity (Women for Health - Procurement of Services) is a component of Women for Health (W4H) Programme reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £33,975,589. This component benefits Nigeria, and works in the following sector(s): Health policy and administrative management, Personnel development for population and reproductive health. , with the following implementing partners: Baker Tilly Nigeria, DAI Global Health. The start date is 01-11-2012 and the end date is 31-10-2020.
